---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "April 2026";
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy | Shakil Traders Limited">
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-slate-700">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-16 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 italic text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 leading-relaxed">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">1. What are Cookies?</h2>
            <p>
              Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device by websites that you visit. 
              They are widely used to make websites work, or work more efficiently, as well as to provide information 
              to the owners of the site.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              <strong>SHAKIL TRADERS LIMITED</strong> uses cookies to enhance your experience on our website and 
              to understand how our wholesale catalog is being used. We use the following types of cookies:
            </p>
            
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-6">
              <table class="w-full text-left text-sm border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                    <th class="py-3 font-bold text-slate-900">Type</th>
                    <th class="py-3 font-bold text-slate-900">Purpose</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold">Strictly Necessary</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-slate-600">Essential for the website to function. These cannot be switched off.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold">Analytical/Performance</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-slate-600">Allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can improve our service (e.g. Google Analytics).</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold">Functional</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-slate-600">Used to recognize you when you return to our website (e.g. remembering your inquiry preferences).</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
            <p>
              In some cases, we use cookies provided by trusted third parties. For example, our website uses:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4 font-light">
              <li><strong>Google Maps:</strong> To show our Whitechapel location.</li>
              <li><strong>Formspree/Netlify:</strong> To process your wholesale inquiries securely.</li>
              <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> To help us understand which produce categories are most popular.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">4. Managing Your Cookies</h2>
            <p>
              Most web browsers allow some control of most cookies through the browser settings. 
              To find out more about cookies, including how to see what cookies have been set and how to manage and delete them, visit 
              <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline">www.aboutcookies.org</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              Please note that if you disable essential cookies, some parts of this website may not function correctly for your business inquiries.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 mt-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Questions?</h2>
            <p class="text-sm">
              If you have any questions regarding our use of cookies, please email us at 
              <span class="font-bold">info@shakiltradersltd.com</span> or write to our registered office: 
              <br/>101 Whitechapel High Street, London, E1 7RA.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 font-medium transition-colors">&larr; Back to Shakil Traders Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>